@wordwrap
@tab 8
   
@node sect0 "Name"
tzxlist - Sinclair ZX Spectrum "real" tape file lister    
@endnode

@node sect1 "Synopsis"
 @{b}tzxlist@{ub} @{i}tapefile@{ui}...     


@endnode

@node sect2 "Description"
tzxlist outputs a description of the contents of TZX, TAP and Warajevo TAP tape files.    
@endnode

@node sect3 "Options"


· @{i}tapefile@{ui} @{lindent 3}
specifies a tape file whose contents are to be listed.    @{lindent 0}


@endnode

@node sect4 "Bugs"
None known.    
@endnode

@node sect5 "See Also"
@{i}fuse@{ui}(1), @{i}fuse-utils@{ui}(1), @{i}listbasic@{ui}(1), @{i}tapeconv@{ui}(1) The comp.sys.sinclair Spectrum FAQ, at 
@{i}http://www.worldofspectrum.org/faq/index.html@{ui}.    


@endnode

@node sect6 "Author"
Philip Kendall (philip-fuse@shadowmagic.org.uk). Darren Salt wrote this man page. 


@endnode
